      "title": "Children talk about the mind",
      "abstract": "1. Children, Mind, and Language: An Introduction 2. Language and Mind: Methods 3. Talk about Thoughts and Beliefs 4. Talk about Desires 5. Desires and Beliefs 6. Explanations and Arguments 7. Individual Differences 8. Children's Developing Theory of Mind 9. Alternatives and Controversies 10. Ordinary Talk about Persons and Minds: Questions and Conclusions References Index"
